    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u go deeper into why the meritocracy argument is basically just a way to avoid dealing with these systemic issues? like, i want to argue that the idea that \"everyone gets what they deserve based on hard work\" is actually just a fallacy used to protect the status quo. how would u frame that in the essay?",
